bradtaniguchi-dev

This repo represents my portfolio/blog site that is hosted on github-pages.

This repo will be updated to replace the current one at: https://github.com/bradtaniguchi/bradtaniguchi.github.io

Which uses a custom domain at: https://bradtaniguchi.dev/

issue.title: [feat] Add projects list
issue.body:
**Describe the solution you'd like**


The project list will be "opt-in" for specific github repos. Along with automatically including the pinned projects from github's profile.

The general layout should follow a similar layout 4 main "cards" and then a table
list of other projects. 

**note** unlike the index, there should be custom data provided via props.

comment.body: This will also include the previous "static" files that were available/added in the old portfolio.
